The Art Of War
https://imageserver.kitapyurdu.com/select.php?imageid=9421070&isWatermarked=true
2019-08-02
 11,25
Written about 2000 years ago, The Art of War is a strategy book which is the most known and keeps up-to-date to be read. Based on advices for commanders about how to behave on a battle the book is still sought after today, because it is not only a war book, it handles art and strategical tendencies as art. For this reason it is regarded as guide in today’s business life. In our era, every division in life has changed into an arena, so The Art of War will be used for a long time.Sun Tzu states from years ago to us via this book in which he grounded on philosophical approach: “To win all the battles isn’t the acme of skill, to subdue the enemy without fighting is the acme of skill.”
